msgid "Accepta"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the theme
#: style.css:5
msgid "Accepta is a modern, lightweight, and highly customizable WordPress theme perfect for businesses, creative agencies, and online stores. Designed with performance and flexibility in mind, it delivers exceptional user experience and optimal loading speeds. The theme features seamless integration with Elementor page builder, allowing you to create stunning layouts without coding. Built-in WooCommerce support makes it ideal for e-commerce websites with beautifully styled product pages, shop layouts, and checkout flows. Accepta offers multiple header layouts, flexible footer options, and a clean, professional design that adapts perfectly to any device. With extensive customization options through the WordPress Customizer, you can easily adjust colors, typography, layouts, and more to match your brand identity. The theme is translation-ready, SEO-optimized, and follows WordPress coding standards for reliability and security. Whether you're building a business website, portfolio, blog, or online shop, Accepta provides the perfect foundation to bring your vision to life."
msgstr ""

